{"tid":787191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅致光說政府研究延長產假或可以補貼促成","createTime":"2018-08-20T12:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T12:55:11.000Z","uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb87a192593b1331b99a20d84779521d5e678cc","tid":787191,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T12:40:53.000Z","msg":"勞工及福利局長羅致光出席亞洲家庭高峰會後說，政府期望在年底前，完成將法定產假由10周延長至14周的研究，由於本港僱主要全數負擔女僱員產假期間工資，政府檢討時面對來自資方的一定阻力，不過政府需要承擔推動的責任，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>其中一個可行方式，是考慮以公帑補貼僱主部分額外支出，補貼比例要再研究。<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n對於行政會議成員張宇人早前曾說「侍產假一日都唔應該有」，羅致光說勞資雙方對勞工問題難免存在分歧，政府會尊重不同意見。<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n同叫個僱員自己拎錢出黎放自己假有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65af8b3a0ef85955e09e63ec0bdb92c7d8f4e28","tid":787191,"uid":126731,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T12:45:18.000Z","msg":"不如直接用公帑幫全香港老闆出糧丫笨."},{"pid":"f1e23253fa40453c1dae221020d3079755879804","tid":787191,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T12:46:18.000Z","msg":"有幾弱智先會做到狗官"},{"pid":"b34b908ae0e74953733f6d80496715b3bdc239cc","tid":787191,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1e23253fa40453c1dae221020d3079755879804","tid":787191,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T12:46:18.000Z","msg":"有幾弱智先會做到狗官"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T12:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條友唔係傳IQ好高架咩 140？"},{"pid":"251281654ca158ad9d4033c4aa701a84231668e1","tid":787191,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b34b908ae0e74953733f6d80496715b3bdc239cc","tid":787191,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1e23253fa40453c1dae221020d3079755879804","tid":787191,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T12:46:18.000Z","msg":"